[{"id":"a4415bbd21b81ced9d3128300f90679a","from":"Lesley Groff","from_email":"lesley@nysgllc.com","to":"J. Epstein","to_list":[{"name":"J. Epstein","email":"jeeproject@yahoo.com"}],"cc_list":[],"subject":"RE: Sikorsky S-76C++","date":"2007-12-13T18:22:55.000Z","formatted_date":"Dec 13, 2007","formatted_time":"6:22 PM","body":"I have relayed.\n\n \n\nFrom: J. Epstein [mailto:jeeproject@yahoo.com] \nSent: Thursday, December 13, 2007 1:22 PM\nTo: Lesley Groff\nSubject: Re: Sikorsky S-76C++\n\n \n\nsplit it 12.95\n\n----- Original Message ----\nFrom: Lesley Groff <lesley@nysgllc.com>\nTo: J. Epstein <jeeproject@yahoo.com>\nSent: Thursday, December 13, 2007 10:12:37 AM\nSubject: FW: Sikorsky S-76C++\n\n \n\n \n\nFrom: Sean J. Lancaster [mailto:bristolgv@earthlink.net] \nSent: Thursday, December 13, 2007 10:08 AM\nTo: lvjet@aol.com; Lesley Groff; Darren Indyke; Lesley Groff\nSubject: FW: Sikorsky S-76C++\n\n \n\nPlease find the offer as per my email this morning.  Please be advised I have told them $13.0 firm on the pricing.  They insist this the maximum they will pay.\n\n \n\nBest regards \n\n \n\n \n\nSean J. Lancaster\n\nBristol Associates Inc.\n\n1-540-665-5135 direct\n\n1-202-682-4000 ext 1130 Main Office\n\n1-540-533-8183 Mobile\n\n1-540-301-0050 FAX\n\nslancaster@bristolassociates.com\n\nwww.bristolassociates.com <http://www.bristolassociates.com/>  \n\n \n\nThis message may contain confidential and/or legally privileged information.  If you are not the intended recipient of the message, please destroy it. Any unauthorized dissemination, distribution or copying of the material in this message, and any attachments to the message, is strictly forbidden. (c) 2007 all rights reserved.\n\n \n\nFrom: Rick Smith [mailto:rsmith@baliaircraft.com] \nSent: Thursday, December 13, 2007 9:18 AM\nTo: slancaster@bristolassociates.com\nSubject: Sikorsky S-76C++\n\n \n\nSean:\n\n \n\nAs promised, attached is our offer for the S-76C++.  We\u2019ve worked extremely hard to get to this point and will appreciate all your efforts to get this deal done.  Please let me know as soon as possible, if you hear from Mr. Epstein.\n\n \n\nRespectfully,\nRick Smith\nVice President\nBusiness Aircraft Leasing, Inc.\n615.361.3781 (ph)\n615.367.1226 (fax)\nwww.baliaircraft.com\n\nThis e-mail and any attachments have been scanned for viruses, but it is the responsibility of the recipient to conduct their own security measures and no responsibility is accepted by BALI for loss or damage arising from the receipt or use of this e-mail.  \n\n \n\n \n\n","body_html":"<html xmlns:v=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml\" xmlns:o=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" xmlns:w=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:word\" xmlns:x=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:excel\" xmlns:p=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:powerpoint\" xmlns:a=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:access\" xmlns:dt=\"uuid:C2F41010-65B3-11d1-A29F-00AA00C14882\" xmlns:s=\"uuid:BDC6E3F0-6DA3-11d1-A2A3-00AA00C14882\" xmlns:rs=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:rowset\" xmlns:z=\"#RowsetSchema\" xmlns:b=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:publisher\" xmlns:ss=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:spreadsheet\" xmlns:c=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:component:spreadsheet\" xmlns:oa=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:activation\" xmlns:html=\"http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40\" xmlns:q=\"http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/envelope/\" xmlns:D=\"DAV:\" xmlns:x2=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/office/excel/2003/xml\" xmlns:ois=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/sharepoint/soap/ois/\" xmlns:dir=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/sharepoint/soap/directory/\" xmlns:ds=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/09/xmldsig#\" xmlns:dsp=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/sharepoint/dsp\" xmlns:udc=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/data/udc\" xmlns:xsd=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema\" xmlns:sps=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/sharepoint/soap/\" xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\" xmlns:udcxf=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/data/udc/xmlfile\" xm